Type: Package
Package: MitoHEAR
Title: Quantification of Mitochondrial DNA Heteroplasmy
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gabriele Lubatti
Maintainer: Gabriele Lubatti <gabriele.lubatti@helmholtz-muenchen.de>
